response.original_title: The Presidents - Quest for the Kingdom
response.overview: The Presidents are tired of their mundane life as the school's biggest losers. They want to start a new place away from the school, a new land where they can live their own lives and be their own kings. Ben, the king of the school, and the cool kids see this as a threat to their power and have other plans…  This movie is the final chapter of “The Presidents”. Brace yourself for a thrilling adventure like no other. The final showdown between the presidents and the cool kids.
response.title: The Presidents - Quest for the Kingdom
